=Episode 21=

3
00:00:35,127 --> 00:00:35,967
Don't move!

4
00:00:35,967 --> 00:00:37,487
- Get down!
- Put your hands up!

5
00:00:39,768 --> 00:00:40,608
Get down!

6
00:00:57,527 --> 00:00:58,607
What are you looking at?

7
00:00:59,007 --> 00:01:00,208
Hurry and pack up.

8
00:01:00,407 --> 00:01:01,527
The police are here.

9
00:01:01,527 --> 00:01:02,848
How could we have been exposed?

10
00:01:02,848 --> 00:01:04,728
Didn't you say that we were well hidden?

11
00:01:04,728 --> 00:01:06,208
I'm about to marry Song Qian.

12
00:01:06,208 --> 00:01:07,447
Now you're telling me to run?

13
00:01:08,368 --> 00:01:09,648
Are you kidding me?

14
00:01:09,648 --> 00:01:11,527
Song Qian is a cop.

15
00:01:12,007 --> 00:01:13,208
You stupid woman!

16
00:01:15,967 --> 00:01:16,807
Brother,

17
00:01:17,447 --> 00:01:18,728
