18
00:01:19,007 --> 00:01:20,208
What do you mean he is a cop?

19
00:01:22,967 --> 00:01:25,120
Look at the surveillance
in the hospital's mezzanine.

20
00:01:25,472 --> 00:01:26,637
Take a look.

21
00:01:26,808 --> 00:01:29,728
He personally led the police
on the drug raid.

22
00:01:29,967 --> 00:01:30,927
Song Qian

23
00:01:31,607 --> 00:01:32,768
is a cop!

24
00:01:34,648 --> 00:01:35,527
Song Qian,

25
00:01:36,007 --> 00:01:37,168
