26
00:01:39,328 --> 00:01:41,648
I'll make that ingrate pay.

27
00:01:42,447 --> 00:01:44,768
I will also get all our goods back.

28
00:01:44,848 --> 00:01:45,688
Move.

29
00:01:46,168 --> 00:01:47,008
Behave yourself.

30
00:01:50,328 --> 00:01:51,168
Mr. Song,

31
00:01:51,567 --> 00:01:52,768
