32
00:01:56,208 --> 00:01:58,248
Deliver the goods
to the East Street dock.

33
00:01:58,567 --> 00:01:59,808
Or I'll kill her.

34
00:01:59,808 --> 00:02:00,808
Song Qian, don't come!

35
00:02:00,808 --> 00:02:01,768
Don't come here!

36
00:02:02,328 --> 00:02:03,328
Shut up!

37
00:02:04,208 --> 00:02:05,048
Song Qian,

38
00:02:05,447 --> 00:02:06,607
