41
00:02:13,768 --> 00:02:15,208
I really regret it.

42
00:02:16,728 --> 00:02:18,407
Back then, to make you
stop investigating,

43
00:02:18,407 --> 00:02:19,768
I gave you the tracker

44
00:02:20,407 --> 00:02:21,808
that led you to him.

45
00:02:22,047 --> 00:02:23,047
But it doesn't matter.

46
00:02:24,728 --> 00:02:26,007
Soon, when Song Qian arrives,

47
00:02:26,007 --> 00:02:27,328
I will kill him.

48
00:02:28,127 --> 00:02:29,527
Then we'll go abroad.

49
00:02:30,047 --> 00:02:30,887
Zhou Shen,

50
00:02:31,728 --> 00:02:33,447
can you wake up?

51
00:02:34,007 --> 00:02:36,648
I'd rather die than go abroad with you.

52
00:02:37,728 --> 00:02:39,248
Then what do you want?

53
00:02:39,248 --> 00:02:40,607
You killed my mom.

54
00:02:40,848 --> 00:02:42,648
And you still dream of being with me?

55
00:02:44,368 --> 00:02:45,728
I didn't mean to kill her.

56
00:02:46,848 --> 00:02:48,728
She discovered my secret.

57
00:02:50,047 --> 00:02:52,007
Now I've discovered your secret too.

58
00:02:52,248 --> 00:02:53,328
Go ahead and kill me.

59
00:02:53,527 --> 00:02:54,447
Like you killed my mom.

60
00:02:54,447 --> 00:02:55,728
Kill me!

61
00:02:56,007 --> 00:02:57,848
Why do you all have to push me?

62
00:03:01,248 --> 00:03:02,248
But rest assured.

63
00:03:04,248 --> 00:03:06,728
I won't let you die easily.

64
00:03:12,007 --> 00:03:12,847
Gu Nian.

65
00:03:13,648 --> 00:03:14,808
You wretch!

66
00:03:15,208 --> 00:03:16,407
You ruined my life.

67
00:03:16,407 --> 00:03:17,848
I won't let you off easily.

68
00:03:17,848 --> 00:03:18,967
Die!

69
00:03:19,368 --> 00:03:20,407
Are you crazy?

70
00:03:21,248 --> 00:03:22,567
If Gu Nian dies,

71
00:03:22,848 --> 00:03:24,328
