72
00:03:24,328 --> 00:03:25,447
dear sister?

73
00:03:25,527 --> 00:03:27,047
She stole my man.

74
00:03:27,208 --> 00:03:28,927
Can I not do anything?

75
00:03:30,967 --> 00:03:32,047
At such a time,

76
00:03:32,047 --> 00:03:33,808
