79
00:03:41,927 --> 00:03:43,607
Nian, be good.

80
00:03:46,007 --> 00:03:47,567
Stop making me angry.

81
00:03:48,447 --> 00:03:50,527
Do you despise me that much?

82
00:03:52,047 --> 00:03:52,967
Boss!

83
00:03:54,368 --> 00:03:55,208
Song Qian is here.

84
00:03:59,848 --> 00:04:01,967
