85
00:04:02,927 --> 00:04:03,767
Qian.

86
00:04:04,047 --> 00:04:04,887
Song Qian.

87
00:04:05,447 --> 00:04:06,728
You know it's a trap.

88
00:04:06,728 --> 00:04:07,768
Yet you still came.

89
00:04:09,768 --> 00:04:10,608
If I didn't come,

90
00:04:11,168 --> 00:04:12,008
