92
00:04:23,808 --> 00:04:25,567
You want your woman, right?

93
00:04:26,328 --> 00:04:27,848
Hand over the goods.

94
00:04:31,407 --> 00:04:32,248
Okay.

95
00:04:37,168 --> 00:04:38,008
